ecodeReportData(...)` and its `Field#set(...)` branches for `String`, `double`, and numeric fields.\n\nFile updated:\n- `tests/src/org.antlr/antlr/3.5.2/src/test/java/org_antlr/antlr/GrammarReportTest.java`\n\nI did not run tests.", "textSignature": "{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0c900ddf1c4ccbcd0169f6a291a8e88192a616cfe2e9074b4b\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 1643, "output": 845, "cacheRead": 33280, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 35768, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "stop", "timestamp": 1777771142259, "responseId": "resp_0c900ddf1c4ccbcd0169f6a286e6248192bd5317111e81a165"}}
